{"blogid": "123463209", "writerAge": "码龄4年", "writerBlogNum": "3", "writerCollect": "18", "writerComment": "1", "writerFan": "11", "writerGrade": "1级", "writerIntegral": "66", "writerName": "浅笑SR", "writerProfileAdress": "writer_image\\profile_123463209.jpg", "writerRankTotal": "181458", "writerRankWeekly": "37417", "writerThumb": "22", "writerVisitNum": "6193", "blog_read_count": "1925", "blog_time": "已于 2022-05-14 21:05:24 修改", "blog_title": "VB.NET连接SQL数据库", "content": "<div class=\"article_content clearfix\" id=\"article_content\">\n<link href=\"style.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<div class=\"markdown_views prism-dracula\" id=\"content_views\">\n<svg style=\"display: none;\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n<path d=\"M5,0 0,2.5 5,5z\" id=\"raphael-marker-block\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" style=\"-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\"></path>\n</svg>\n<p></p>\n<div class=\"toc\">\n<h3>VB.NET与SQL数据库的数据互通</h3>\n<ul><li><a href=\"#_5\">一、准备工作</a></li><li><a href=\"#VBNET_13\">二、VB.NET操作、代码、可能遇到的问题等</a></li></ul>\n</div>\n<p></p>\n<hr/>\n<h1><a id=\"_5\"></a>一、准备工作</h1>\n<p>①本地网络连接的IP地址；<br/> ②已安装好的SQL软件(本例使用SQL2014)；<br/> ③已安装好的Visual Studio 2019软件；<br/> ④用于VB.NET连接的数据库(登录名称、密码、数据库)；<br/> <img alt=\"数据库登录名称和密码\" src=\"image\\6faecd014bb34b168921bb861b3573cf.png\"/><br/> <img alt=\"数据库\" src=\"image\\2ad67ddc990d4ceb9aa0c183131de5a3.png\"/></p>\n<hr/>\n<h1><a id=\"VBNET_13\"></a>二、VB.NET操作、代码、可能遇到的问题等</h1>\n<p>1.打开Visual Studio 2019新建VB.NET窗体应用，如下图：<br/> <img alt=\"新建VB.NET项目\" src=\"image\\984b70f095834b1baf23c603361e7e33.png\"/></p>\n<hr/>\n<p>2.配置新项目信息，如下图：<br/> <img alt=\"配置新项目\" src=\"image\\cb3bd63f14a444c6a99c3ad21e3152c5.png\"/></p>\n<hr/>\n<p>3.窗体界面设计，4个Label，4个TextBox，1个Button，如下图：<br/> <img alt=\"界面设计\" src=\"image\\ff5be8c926dd4c709ae14f6296e9a322.png\"/></p>\n<hr/>\n<p>4.代码设计：</p>\n<pre><code class=\"prism language-vbnet\"><span class=\"token keyword\">Imports</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">System</span>.<span class=\"token keyword\">Data</span>.SqlClient\n<span class=\"token keyword\">Public</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">Class</span> SqlForVBNET\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">Private</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">Sub</span> ConTest_Click<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>sender <span class=\"token keyword\">As</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">Object</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> e <span class=\"token keyword\">As</span> EventArgs<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">Handles</span> ConTest.Click\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">Try</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">Dim</span> Cn <span class=\"token keyword\">As</span> SqlConnection <span class=\"token comment\">'数据库连接对象</span>\n            <span class=\"token keyword\">Dim</span> Database <span class=\"token keyword\">As</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">String</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"data source=\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span> LocalIPaddress.<span class=\"token function\">Text</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span><span class=\"token comment\">'本地网络IP</span>\n                                     <span class=\"token string\">\";database=\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span> SQLname.<span class=\"token function\">Text</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span><span class=\"token comment\">'数据库名称</span>\n                                     <span class=\"token string\">\";uid=\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span> SQLlodaName.<span class=\"token function\">Text</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span><span class=\"token comment\">'数据库登录名称</span>\n                                     <span class=\"token string\">\";pwd=\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span> SQLlodaPassword.<span class=\"token function\">Text</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span> <span class=\"token string\">\";\"</span> <span class=\"token comment\">'数据库登录密码</span>\n            <span class=\"token function\">Debug</span>.<span class=\"token function\">Print</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Database<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n            Cn <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">New</span> SqlConnection<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span>Database<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n            Cn.<span class=\"token keyword\">Open</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n            Cn.<span class=\"token keyword\">Close</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n            MsgBox<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"数据库连接成功\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"提示\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">Catch</span> err <span class=\"token keyword\">As</span> Exception\n            MsgBox<span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"数据库连接不成功!\"</span> <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span> vbCrLf <span class=\"token operator\">&amp;</span> err.Message<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"提示\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span>\n        <span class=\"token keyword\">End</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">Try</span>\n    <span class=\"token keyword\">End</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">Sub</span>\n<span class=\"token keyword\">End</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">Class</span>\n</code></pre>\n<p>5.测试连接，可能出现的结果：<br/> 5.1连接成功，如下图：<br/> <img alt=\"连接数据库成功\" src=\"image\\75e5a68ad94545a1a29fdccf8de1f773.png\"/><br/> 5.2连接失败，如下图，可能原因：<br/> 错误分析：一段时间后弹出，IP地址未设置正确或数据库服务未启动<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"image\\3f4b044af33a4a2fa1648def87ce8ce2.png\"/></p>\n<p>5.3连接失败，如下图，可能原因：<br/> 错误分许：一段时间后弹出，数据库名称未设置正确<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"image\\e50ae87fb4924d72b6c3e6936cf797c5.png\"/><br/> 5.4连接失败，如下图，可能原因：<br/> 错误分析：一段时间后弹出，数据库登录名称未设置正确<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"image\\8d45e52bd9d241b89c135bdeca9b2cdb.png\"/><br/> 5.5连接失败，如下图，可能原因<br/> 错误分许：一段时间后弹出，数据库登录密码未设置正确<br/> <img alt=\"在这里插入图片描述\" src=\"image\\f4381200579f43f386f2a926572e37f6.png\"/></p>\n<hr/>\n<p>愿你不要屈从于命运的安排，坚韧不拔，锲而不舍，做永远的生活强者！</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>.net平台下C#和VB.NET很相似，本文也可为C#提供一定的参考。</p>\n<hr/>\n</div>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/editerView/markdown_views-22a2fefd3b.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n<link href=\"https://csdnimg.cn/release/blogv2/dist/mdeditor/css/style-4f8fbf9108.css\" rel=\"stylesheet\"/>\n</div>"}